Package aston.nabneyit.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Product
    Defines interface that any product used in the factory must implement
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Connector
    Defines the general form of a connector between units in a factory.
    IntelligentRouter
    Defines the only type of Connector needed for the coursework.
    Layer
    Groups some units into a layer; this is a convenient way of structuring the factory needed for the coursework.
    LayeredFactory
    Defines a factory as a series of layers, with each unit in each layer connected to unit(s) in the next layer.
    Machine
    Implements a general machine class that carries out a process of some timespan on the first item in the queue that represents its input line.
    Sink
    Defines a sink for the factory.
    SinkTest  
    Source
    Models the arrival of new food items in the factory.
    SourceTest  
    Unit
    Defines the abstract base class for the processing units in a Factory.
